可考虑迁移至现代邮件客户端如 Thunderbird 或 Mutt。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88609666024181&w=2","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#elm","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1334.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1334","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1334.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9pwm-wh34-fpxm/GHSA-9pwm-wh34-fpxm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001031.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1334.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1050.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1051","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1051.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1335","title":"Red Hat Linux cmu-snmp snmpd 配置错误漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 4.0 系统中 cmu-snmp 软件包 3.3-1 之前版本的 snmpd 服务器存在配置错误漏洞。由于默认配置不当，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞对目标系统上的敏感信息进行读取或写入操作，导致信息泄露或系统配置被篡改。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 4.0 及使用相关 cmu-snmp 组件的系统，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1335"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.290","remediation":"升级 cmu-snmp 软件包至 3.3-1 或更高版本，并修改 SNMP 配置文件 /etc/snmp/snmpd.conf，将默认 public/private 团体字改为复杂随机字符串；同时在 iptables 防火墙中限制仅信任 IP 可访问 UDP 161 端口，禁用 SNMP 写权限（read-only）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh40-errata-general.html#cmu-snmp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7251","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1335","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1335.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pr33-x2p7-6w2x/GHSA-pr33-x2p7-6w2x.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001032.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--54c919b9-3bdc-4906-ba93-56a73c55a239.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1051.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1055","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1055.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1339","title":"Linux 和 FreeBSD NAT 记录路由请求拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux 2.2.10 及更早版本（使用 ipchains）以及 FreeBSD 3.2（使用 ipfw）的网络地址转换（NAT）功能存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 ping -R（记录路由）ICMP 数据包，触发内核在处理路由记录选项时出现异常，导致系统内核崩溃（kernel panic）。该漏洞攻击条件简单，无需认证即可远程触发，影响运行上述版本 Linux 及 FreeBSD 操作系统的网络设备。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1339"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.823","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.11 及以上版本，或升级 FreeBSD 至 3.3 及以上版本。对于仍运行此类老旧系统的环境，建议迁移至受支持的现代版本（如 Linux 6.x 或 FreeBSD 13.x），并在防火墙层面过滤 ICMP 带记录路由选项（record route）的数据包作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93277426802802&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93277766505061&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7257.php","http://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v2.2/patch-2.2.11.gz","http://www.osvdb.org/6105","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1339.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1339","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1339.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1339.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8m8f-vqxq-q9r6/GHSA-8m8f-vqxq-q9r6.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87884/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4321c2f2-9dc5-429a-bd37-0385455013c1.json","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1339.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1055.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1072","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1072.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1355","title":"Compaq Management Agents for Servers 弱配置默认口令漏洞","description":"Compaq Insight Management Agent 4.23及之前版本、Management Agents for Servers 4.40及之前版本在安装BMC Patrol组件时，会自动创建一个名为PFCUser的默认账户，该账户使用固定默认密码且拥有过高系统权限。远程攻击者可利用此默认凭证登录目标系统，获取未授权访问权限，进而执行恶意操作。该漏洞影响大量Compaq/HP服务器管理系统，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1355"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.847","remediation":"升级 Compaq Insight Management Agent 至 4.23 以上版本，或 Management Agents for Servers 至 4.40 以上版本；同时删除或禁用默认创建的 PFCUser 账户，并修改所有相关账户的默认口令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93542118727732&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93654336516711&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93759822430801&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94183795025294&w=2","http://www.compaq.com/products/servers/management/advisory.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3231","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1355.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1355","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1355.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1355.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qmhx-84gq-mqf3/GHSA-qmhx-84gq-mqf3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87874/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1355.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--203e8cbd-6b3c-4878-8673-6db7c739ac0c.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/SecurityTapestry-Queen/nvd-cve-api-search/blob/6901bdceb94c779e36bd5f694ddd48cafcd5c8d3/archive/2025-04-06/report-04-06-2025-20-58-46.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1072.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1075","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1075.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1358","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 本地策略绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 系统中，当管理员修改用户策略时，若本地 ntconfig.pol 文件对用户不可写入，策略无法正确更新，导致本地用户可通过将该策略文件设为只读等方式绕过系统强制执行的访问限制。该漏洞允许低权限用户在未授权情况下提升操作权限，危害系统安全策略的完整性。攻击者需要具有本地登录权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1358"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.220","remediation":"确保 ntconfig.pol 文件的 NTFS 权限正确配置，仅允许 Administrators 完全控制，禁止普通用户具有写入权限。建议升级到 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本，后续版本的策略应用机制已修复此问题。如无法升级，可定期检查 ntconfig.pol 文件权限完整性并启用审计策略监控异常权限变更。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q157/6/73.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7400.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1358.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1358","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1358.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1358.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m4fw-6g2w-g44w/GHSA-m4fw-6g2w-g44w.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84433/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1358.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001035.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1075.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1076","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1076.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1359","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Ntconfig.pol 策略安全绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 存在安全策略绕过漏洞。当服务器主机名超过 13 个字符时，系统无法正确解析 Ntconfig.pol 文件中的全局组策略配置，导致已设限制策略无法生效。攻击者利用该漏洞可绕过管理员设定的安全策略获取非授权访问权限，影响 Windows NT 系列系统。此漏洞源于系统在处理长主机名时策略引擎的异常行为，无需特殊工具即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1359"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.343","remediation":"将服务器主机名缩短至 13 个字符以内，确保 Ntconfig.pol 全局组策略正常生效。安装微软 KB Q163875 提供的 hotfix 补丁以彻底修复该问题。鉴于 Windows NT 已停止安全支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q163/8/75.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7401.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1359.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1359","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1359.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1359.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7hww-85g7-g9hc/GHSA-7hww-85g7-g9hc.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87900/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1359.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/4a6e09a063689f2d97734100478c1eef6f6dc387/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1076.toml"}]